          <p>Anying will use commercially-reasonable efforts to process the Customer transactions in an expeditious manner. Anying cannot control and is not responsible for the time it takes financial institutions to settle accounts. If a transaction is processed on the next business day for whatever reason, Anying will not, in the absence of gross negligence or wilful misconduct, be responsible for failure, delays or errors in the completion of the transaction.</p></small>

        <h5>8.12 Rejection of Trade</h5>

